ists.	\N	2025-06-26 04:00:00+00	2025-06-26 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.20357", "title": "REF EAT (Reasoning type Exploration for Feature Discovery)"}]	{"KDI School of Public Policy and Management",KAIST,GIST}
