ans use DiaLLMs for real-time patient assessments. The AI-driven system aids in recommending lab tests, interpreting results, and suggesting diagnoses during patient consultations, greatly improving workflow efficiency and diagnostic accuracy.	\N	2025-06-26 04:00:00+00	2025-06-26 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.20059", "title": "DiaLLMs"}]	{"Pennsylvania State University College of Information Sciences and Technology","Salesforce AI Research"}
