sical feedback is required for downstream quantum algorithms.	https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a4/Seal_of_the_California_Institute_of_Technology.svg/300px-Seal_of_the_California_Institute_of_Technology.svg.png	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.21345", "title": "QuantumComm"}]	{"University of California, Davis","Institute for Quantum Computing","Quantum Computing Research Lab, Google","Department of Computer Science, MIT"}
