g consultations or treatment planning based on the VBT analysis. Enhancing the understanding of individual brain behaviors through personalized models that have been trained on anonymized data.	\N	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.21155", "title": "Amortized Virtual Brain Twins"}]	{"Aix Marseille University",INSERM,"Institute of Neuroscience Systems"}
