periments, improving the reliability of biological modeling in environmental and health sciences.	\N	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.02581", "title": "BioDynamics Estimator"}]	{"University of Tennessee Knoxville - Department of Mathematics","University of Tennessee Knoxville - Department of Microbiology"}
