onments for real-time seizure detection and for providing BCI control commands in rehabilitation where patients can control prostheses through imagined movements.	https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c5/Hustseals.png/360px-Hustseals.png	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.21140", "title": "DBConformer BCI"}]	{"Huazhong University of Science and Technology","Shenzhen Huazhong University of Science and Technology Research Institute"}
