ential crosstalk and misleading interpretations.	The framework can be used for setting up robust quantum experiments by research institutions to validate quantum theories. It is also applicable in commercial settings for quantum cryptography and secure communications, where loophole-free quantum states are essential.	https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/31/POL_University_of_Warsaw_logo.svg/400px-POL_University_of_Warsaw_logo.svg.png	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.08940", "title": "Quantum Objectivity Checker"}]	{"University of Warsaw","Institute of Applied Computational Sciences","Center for Theoretical Physics, Polish Academy of Sciences"}
