tive dynamics, allowing researchers to obtain reliable solutions faster than classical methods.	https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/04/Utoronto_coa.svg/420px-Utoronto_coa.svg.png	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.20760", "title": "QuantumODE Solver"}]	{"University of Toronto","Apollo Quantum LLC","Zapata AI Inc.","Pacific Northwest National Laboratory"}
