mponents where reliable adhesion under varied environmental conditions is critical. Potential use in healthcare for creating dependable medical adhesive patches or wearable devices.	https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Arms_of_University_of_Oxford.svg/500px-Arms_of_University_of_Oxford.svg.png	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	2025-06-27 04:00:00+00	[{"url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.20745", "title": "Mushroom Adhesive Technology"}]	{"University of Oviedo","University of Oxford","University of California, Santa Barbara","University of Aberdeen","INM – Leibniz Institute for New Materials"}
